Modern Contact Form with Real-Time Validation
Project Name: Contact Form Application
Version: 1.0.0
Last Updated: November 2025
Developer: Web Development Team
Overview
A fully functional, responsive contact form built with pure HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This project demonstrates client-side form validation, modern UI/UX principles, and accessible web design practices.
Purpose
To provide a ready-to-use contact form solution for websites, portfolios, and web applications that need to collect user feedback, inquiries, or general communication from visitors.
Key Features
✅ Real-Time Validation - Instant feedback as users type
✅ Email Format Verification - Ensures valid email addresses
✅ Character Counter - 500 character limit with live tracking
✅ Responsive Design - Works on desktop, tablet, and mobile
✅ Animated Feedback - Smooth transitions and error animations
✅ Success Confirmation - Clear visual feedback on submission
✅ Accessibility - WCAG compliant with proper labels and semantic HTML
✅ No Dependencies - Pure vanilla JavaScript, no libraries required
Technologies Used

HTML5 - Semantic markup and form structure
CSS3 - Modern styling with flexbox, gradients, and animations
JavaScript (ES6) - Form validation and interactive features

Technical Specifications

Browser Support: Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge (latest versions)
Responsive Breakpoints: Works from 320px to 4K displays
Performance: Lightweight (~5KB total file size)
Validation: Client-side only (server-side integration ready)

Project Files
contact-form/
├── index.html       (2.5 KB) - Main structure
├── styles.css       (2.0 KB) - Styling and animations
├── script.js        (2.5 KB) - Validation logic
├── README.md        - Setup instructions
